    <h2>Signs Your Warrandyte Chimney Needs Cleaning</h2>
    <p>If any of these sound familiar, it is time to book:</p>
    <div class="reason-grid">
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128293;</span><div class="rc-title">Smoke coming back in</div><div class="rc-desc">Most common sign of a blocked or sooted flue. A clean usually fixes it immediately.</div></div>
